---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="" class="hero-logo" width="200" height="124">
    <h1>Midland Cycling Club</h1>
    <p>Friendly group rides around Perth's eastern suburbs and beyond. Whether you're new to cycling or a seasoned rider, there's a group for you.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/join/" class="btn btn--primary">Join the Club</a>
      <a href="/rides/" class="btn btn--outline">View Rides</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ride With Us</h2>
    <p>We run group rides every weekend and regular midweek sessions through the summer months.</p>
    <div class="ride-groups">
      <div class="ride-group">
        <h3>Social Ride</h3>
        <div class="meta">Saturdays &middot; 9:00 AM &middot; 30&ndash;50 km</div>
        <p>Relaxed pace, no-drop ride. Perfect for beginners or anyone who fancies an easy spin.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ride-group">
        <h3>Club Ride</h3>
        <div class="meta">Sundays &middot; 8:30 AM &middot; 60&ndash;100 km</div>
        <p>Steady tempo through the lanes. A good mix of flat and rolling terrain.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ride-group">
        <h3>Fast Group</h3>
        <div class="meta">Sundays &middot; 8:00 AM &middot; 80&ndash;120 km</div>
        <p>Brisk pace for experienced riders. Chain-gang skills and longer distances.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Latest News</h2>
    <p>What's been happening at the club.</p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {%- for post in collections.posts.slice(0, 3) %}
      <div class="card">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateFormat }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
